{"data":[{"date":"07:04 30/07","title":"Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/ronaldo-tro-lai-juventus-tap-luyen-cung-dong-doi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG v\u00e0 gi\u1edd m\u1edbi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Turin.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 5 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a qua, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd chia tay CLB. Sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Juventus b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi Ronaldo. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro (88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) t\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y minh ch\u1ee9ng cho tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Cristiano-Ronaldo-tro-lai-Juventus-tap-luyen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u&nbsp;Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n7 n\u0103m qua, Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A song kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Bianconeri l\u00e0 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i vinh quang \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau 22 n\u0103m v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u00f4m qua, Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. H\u1eadu World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p th\u00eam ng\u00e0y ph\u00e9p v\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cristiano ronaldo\" title=\"cristiano ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cristiano-ronaldo.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Benfica, cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan t\u1eeb d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 MLS v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u1ee7a Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Paulo Dybala, Douglas Costa, Rodrigo Bentancur, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca, Blaise Matuidi v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong phi\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bld-mu-ngan-can-mourinho-chieu-mo-sandro-172-192120.html\">BL\u0110 MU ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mourinho chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/xac-dinh-doi-thu-dau-tien-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-tren-dat-y-176-192108.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4810","checkdouble":"192282"},{"date":"08:53 30/07","title":"HLV Toshiya Miura tin \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u00f4m h\u1eadn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/22/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic 2020 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u00e8n gi\u0169a, t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/hlv-toshiya-miura-noi-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang tuy\u1ebfn tr\u1ebb U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Toshiya Miura cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D: \"Theo t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft th\u00ec Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U21 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Miura c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u1ea3 quan khi gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup 2017, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Miura t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-u23-viet-nam-lai-duoc-vinh-danh-tren-bao-nuoc-ngoai-168-192270.html\">\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh tr\u00ean b\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-168-192269.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201ch\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-tin-se-duoc-thay-park-giu-lai-168-192239.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien-168-192236.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duc-chinh-hoan-thien-ban-than-nho-thay-park-thich-da-cap-voi-cong-phuong-168-192232.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u1edd th\u1ea7y Park, th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-truot-bai-kiem-tra-the-luc-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192230.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4809","checkdouble":"192292"},{"date":"08:33 30/07","title":"HLV Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Niko Kovac kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lewandowski s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bayern m\u1eb7c cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c.</h2><h2>Lewandowski \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Bayern</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lewandowski l\u00e0 Pini Zahavi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Allianz Arena. V\u00e0 HLV Kovac c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft mong mu\u1ed1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Lewandowski \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Bernabeu, c\u00e1i t\u00ean Lewandowski l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Real b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCEO Hans-Joachim Watzke c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed5 th\u00eam d\u1ea7u v\u00e0o l\u1eeda khi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Lewandowski tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a.</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Kovac b\u00e1c b\u1ecf tin \u0111\u1ed3n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Kovac ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Kovac ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV&nbsp;Kovac ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n Lewandowski r\u1eddi Bayern</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho th\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-duc/4-diem-den-ly-tuong-neu-lewandowski-roi-bayern-munich-193-187814.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lewandowski r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Bayern</span> kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Kovac ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Lewandowski. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Bayern v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tu\u1ed9t kh\u1ecfi tay m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Lewandowski l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Lewandowski c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Lewandowski c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 l\u00e0 bao l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018-329-192238.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 2-3 Man City (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tan-hlv-bayern-munich-nguong-mo-nguoi-cu-pep-guardiola-184-192215.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Bayern Munich ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4808","checkdouble":"192288"},{"date":"08:07 30/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/30/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-307-lo-dien-ben-do-bat-ngo-cua-hau-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 30/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern: PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Boateng. </strong>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Thiago Silva. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 M.U.</strong> Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft Napoli \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Manchester United cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Matteo Darmian. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n sau 2 n\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 307 L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/sao-mu-chinh-thuc-duoc-hoi-mua-boi-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. </strong>M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan mu\u1ed1n l\u0129nh kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng thua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh. </strong>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Simeone thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Vrsaljko \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. </strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sime Vrsaljko \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. HLV Diego Simeone hy v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" title=\"Sime Vrsaljko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/sao-atletico-madrid-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-khoac-ao-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Vrsaljko trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 sao tr\u1ebb ra \u0111i. </strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Rosenborg cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pedro Chirivella. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 m\u1edbi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Bale.</strong> Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1c b\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Tottenham t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho hay Spurs kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>CLB h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch mua Ojo c\u1ee7a Liverpool. </strong>Middlesbrough \u0111ang m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sheyi Ojo t\u1eeb Liverpool. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Fulham m\u01b0\u1ee3n nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t. Ngo\u00e0i Boro, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Nottingham Forest c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd Ojo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4807","checkdouble":"192287"},{"date":"08:31 30/07","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Digne mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLucas Digne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Alba, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca. 2 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Xac-nhan-Lucas-Digne-roi-Barca-cap-ben-Everton-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Lucas Digne mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Digne kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb HLV Ernesto Valverde, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Lucas Digne \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Barca c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, song vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Barca y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Digne</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Digne, trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca xac nhan Digne cap ben Everton\" title=\"Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Digne c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/barca-xac-nhan-ban-digne-cho-everton-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Digne s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\" target=\"_blank\">Lucas Digne r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton </span>\u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, twitter c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eafp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia v\u00e0 Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Digne v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 xin ph\u00e9p Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDigne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 3 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 4. \u1ede s\u00e2n Goodison Park, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Leighton Baines.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Digne s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Everton d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Marco Silva, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng chia tay Wayne Rooney v\u00e0 Ramiro Funes Mori.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4806","checkdouble":"192286"},{"date":"08:50 30/07","title":"T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal nh\u1eafm Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, song r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-muon-mua-Courtois-va-Willian-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Hazard, n\u1ebfu Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Los Blancos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed theo AS, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-khong-muon-mua-hazard-180-192194.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Hazard</span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos quanh Isco thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u00f4i v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea c\u00e0ng cao, The Blues v\u1eabn \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Courtois v\u00e0 Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Willian, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Thay v\u00ec mua Hazard th\u00ec Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real tinh chi 100 trieu bang mua Courtois va Willian\" title=\"Real t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real t\u00ednh chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Courtois v\u00e0 Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, n\u1ebfu The Blues kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c mua Willian. Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian, song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Los Blancos h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u00e0 Willian, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4805","checkdouble":"192290"},{"date":"07:31 30/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/chelsea-sap-vo-mong-chieu-mo-tuyen-thu-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u1edd Sunday Times \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;h\u00e0ng hot&rdquo;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, Jordan Pickford b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd khi m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Anh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong khung th\u00e0nh Tam s\u01b0, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua Croatia trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup, Pickford nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u1eefng Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Jordan-Pickford-sap-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Chelsea khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 trong m\u01a1 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Sunday Times m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Bayern v\u00e0 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng. Jordan Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"jordan pickford\" title=\"jordan pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/jordan-pickford-cua-Everton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Pickford s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Everton b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pickford t\u1eeb Sunderland. Th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u1edbi giao k\u00e8o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n, Everton c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gia t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Pickford v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Everton tham gia v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League v\u1edbi Wolves ng\u00e0y 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/drinkwater-muon-roi-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-192252.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c Stamford Bridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-olivier-giroud-172-192243.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Olivier Giroud</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chelsea-bat-ngo-muon-so-huu-ngoi-sao-cua-arsenal-187-192241.html\">Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4804","checkdouble":"192283"},{"date":"07:58 30/07","title":"Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u201csao x\u1ecbt\u201d World Cup, M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/hlv-kovac-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-lewandowski-roi-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan mu\u1ed1n l\u0129nh kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng thua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Bayern Munich x\u1ea5u \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i chia tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Cezary Kucharski b\u1eb1ng Pini Zahavi c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng minh cho vi\u1ec7c anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin uy t\u00edn t\u1eeb \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 Bayern n\u00edu k\u00e9o, Lewandowski v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u00fd ra \u0111i. T\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Lewy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 30, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/muon-co-lewandowski-mu-phai-lam-duoc-dieu-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;Lewandowski c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Bayern</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua, Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Ba Lan d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, anh v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a h\u1ebft Real Madrid l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3i chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho M.U trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lewandowski \u1edf ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Zahavi c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o n\u1ebfu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-0-0-SJ-Earthquakes-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski, ngang v\u1edbi Sanchez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u1edd Daily Star m\u1edbi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng: M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Dortmund \u0111ang nh\u1eadn 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n t\u1eeb Bayern. Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, Lewandowski mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed1c 500 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n m\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u0129nh. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Lewy v\u1edbi Bayern hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-chinh-thuc-duoc-hoi-mua-boi-napoli-172-192275.html\">Sao M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua b\u1edfi Napoli</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/leicester-hoi-mua-lascelles-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-192200.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-ban-willian-cho-mu-172-192197.html\">N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n &ldquo;tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng&rdquo; Mourinho cho M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-ngoai-hang-anh-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-172-192177.html\">T\u00e2n binh Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/luke-shaw-khong-gia-han-hop-dong-day-la-ly-do-172-192154.html\">Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4803","checkdouble":"192284"},{"date":"08:16 30/07","title":"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/mu-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-harry-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Vuot-mat-MU,-Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Harry-Maguire-hinh-anh.jpg\"><br>\r\n            \u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maguire \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Maguire s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-san-sang-pha-ky-luc-chuyen-nhuong-de-chieu-mo-ngoi-sao-tuyen-anh-172-192100.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/MU-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-muc-tieu-65-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Harry Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Sergio Ramos. Los Blancos c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1eeb 60 \u0111\u1ebfn 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3, n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Maguire th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Leicester \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ti\u1ec1n, Maguire s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4802","checkdouble":"192285"},{"date":"08:52 30/07","title":"David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/david-luiz-mong-muon-o-lai-chelsea-pho-ta-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri.</h2><h2>David Luiz h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1eeda \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Conte v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 17 tr\u1eadn m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Conte ra \u0111i, David Luiz \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u00e3 qua. Luiz thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/david-luiz-mong-muon-o-lai-chelsea-pho-ta-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>David Luiz mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Khi t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb Paris, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i y\u00eau tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e2ng cao, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u. HLV Sarri lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Luiz \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o Jorginho</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 k\u00edch n\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d mang t\u00ean Jorginho v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues. V\u00e0 David Luiz tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd g\u1ed1c Brazil n\u00e0y th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, lu\u00f4n \u1edf nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-vo-mong-chieu-mo-tuyen-thu-anh-172-192283.html\">Chelsea s\u1eafp v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4801","checkdouble":"192289"},{"date":"06:15 30/07","title":"R\u1eddi Juventus, Buffon mi\u1ec5n lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/roi-juventus-buffon-mien-luon-binh-luan-ve-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bianconeri gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0ng quan v\u1edbi Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, HLV Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho Juventus\u201d. Theo \u00f4ng, \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u00e0 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 Juventus s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Gianluigi Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 40 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Juve sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Paris Saint-Germain d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Buffon-va-Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Buffon kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Juve \u0111ang l\u00e0m b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3\u201d, Buffon n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cJuventus l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 PSG v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c t\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a Juventus sau 22 n\u0103m. Danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u sao Juve kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c anh r\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u00dd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1edfi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t\u201d, Buffon n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cH\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb k\u00edch th\u00edch b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 PSG. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng sau 40 n\u0103m \u1edf Italia, s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p b\u1edfi t\u00f4i \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/allegri-su-co-mat-cua-ronaldo-gay-hai-cho-juventus-176-192193.html\">Allegri: \u201cS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho Juventus\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bld-mu-ngan-can-mourinho-chieu-mo-sandro-172-192120.html\">BL\u0110 MU ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mourinho chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4800","checkdouble":"192279"},{"date":"20:01 29/07","title":"Th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Campuchia, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thang-nhe-campuchia-hlv-doi-tuyen-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Campuchia. V\u00e0 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Campuch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Campuch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/hlv-u16-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-de-campuchia-gay-kho-khan-lon1532863898.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Campuchia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 29/7, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U16 Campuchia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 tung ra v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 duy\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u00edt sao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00ec l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1i b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00ean ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thanh tho\u00e1t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Campuchia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00fang t\u00fang khi ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 g\u1eb7p Timor Leste&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 31/7 t\u1edbi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Timor Leste tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng U16 Indonesia (2/8), Philippines (4/8) v\u00e0 Myanmar (6/8).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4799","checkdouble":"192266"},{"date":"21:26 29/07","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201ch\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7\" c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u0111ang cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo&nbsp;s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 'b\u00e0i t\u1ee7' c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh cho&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng d\u1ecdc v\u00e0 khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n theo c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c theo k\u00e8m.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc l\u1ecfm b\u00e0i t\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/3796019017954803772340125875540635594784768newiy-crop-15327648207251944130715.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n, \u0110T Anh ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 28/7, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n theo &quot;mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh&quot; n\u00e0y. B\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m quen \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00e1c pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh hay V\u0103n H\u1eadu. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp th\u00e0nh th\u1ee5c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m PVF cho \u0111\u1ebfn 31/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 H\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Palestine, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-tin-se-duoc-thay-park-giu-lai-168-192239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/9/15/taninhu19.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-tin-se-duoc-thay-park-giu-lai-168-192239.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 28/7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien-168-192236.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-dau-tien-168-192236.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span><br />\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&#10;\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4798","checkdouble":"192269"}]}